obj_root_law_sections_217_a_content:
  string
  line ^1
  line `[217A. Renewal of permits, driving licences and registration granted under the Motor Vehicles`
  line `Act, 1939.--Notwithstanding the repeal by sub-section (1) of section 217 of the enactments referred to in`
  line `that sub-section, any certificate of fitness or registration or licence or permit issued or granted under the`
  line `said enactments may be renewed under this Act.]`
